modName: Lanterns of Skryim - COT Nights Lvl 1 Preset
summary: Lanterns of Skyrim and CoT v3.1 Nights level 1 preset
descriptionHtml:
Using throb23s preset for level 8 nights and MannyGTs Level 1 nights, I tweaked the settings for less spotlight and more dim spreading light for a nice ambiance while providing sufficient light. :)


Thanks to everyone below for their excellent work! 
Lanterns of Skyrim - All In One by MannyGT
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/18916
